### Tender Notice: Camera Surveillance Systems {#tender-notice-camera-surveillance-systems}
#### Overview {#overview}

Public Services and Procurement Canada (PSPC) invites qualified Offerors to submit Offers for the supply and installation of two (2) Camera Surveillance Systems, along with After-Installation Technical Support. 

#### Tender Information {#tender-information}

* **Reference Number**: CB-428-6965908
* **Solicitation Number**: SPMD-23-WCSS/A
* **Tender Closing Date**: *Open date* - 2023-10-12T14:00:00
* **Expected Contract Start Date**: 2023-11-01
* **Expected Contract End Date**: 2024-10-31

#### Description {#description}

The requirement is described in detail in the solicitation documents and Annexes. PSPC seeks the supply of two camera surveillance systems, along with installation services and required after-installation technical support. The location of delivery is Halifax, Nova Scotia.

#### Tender Process {#tender-process}

The solicitation will be conducted in two phases:

1. Phase I: Technical Bids
2. Phase II: Financial Bids

All qualified Offerors are invited to submit their Technical Bids. Subsequently, responsive Offerors will be invited to submit their Financial Bids. 

#### Required Documents {#required-documents}

All Offerors are required to submit their Offers in accordance with the requirements outlined in the solicitation documents and Annexes. 

#### Contact Information {#contact-information}

* Name: Daphne Klassen-Hayes
* Email: [daphne.klassen-hayes@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca](mailto:daphne.klassen-hayes@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca)
* Phone: 16132960230

#### Notice and Attachments {#notice-and-attachments}

All Notice documents and attachments can be found on the [Canada Buys](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/){target="blank"} website.

#### Notes {#notes}

Please note that Requests for Proposal is open to Offerors worldwide. Registration with IntegrityBC is not required.

